kpi.name: M1002C515

kpi_info.title: UL DCH SELECTED FOR INTERACTIVE DUE TO MAX HSUPA USERS
kpi_info.use: The number of times when E-DCH uplink transport channel cannot be selected in this cell for an interactive class connection due to maximum amount of E-DCH users in the cell or in the local cell group. When E-DCH cannot be selected as uplink transport channel in this cell because the number of E-DCH users in cell would exceed the limit defined by MaxNumberEDCHCell or the number of E-DCH users in local cell group would exceed MaxNumberEDCHLCG.

kpi.kpi_alias: UL DCH SELECTED FOR INTERACTIVE DUE TO MAX HSUPA USERS
